        "message": "LU-8367 tests: long waiting for multistripe file creation\n\nThis test reproduces hang during multistripe file creation.\n 1) reserve object for OST0\n 2) delay reserve object for OST1 (simulate no object)\n 3) failover OST0\nAs result osp_precreate_cleanup_orphans() hangs until the creation\nof all stripes is finished. This leads to impossibility for object\nallocation at OST0.\nFor two multistripe files, when first reserved OST0 and second\nreserved OST1, reconnect. Both file creations will sleep OBD_TIMEOUT.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey.lyashkov@seagate.com>\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Boyko <alexander.boyko@seagate.com>\nSigned-off-by: Sergey Cheremencev <sergey.cheremencev@seagate.com>\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-3623\nChange-Id: I2202825dd7dee298934442b50984cb7413e5f1f4\n"
